text: Adhora Khan is a Bangladeshi film actress and model. ==Career== Adhora made her film debut in Nayok, released on October 19, 2018. Her co-star of the film was Bappy Chowdhury. A week later, on October 26, 2018 her second film Matal was released, co-starring Symon Sadik. ==Filmography== {| class="wikitable sortable" |- !Year !Film !Role !Notes |- | 2018 | Nayok | Parisha | Debut film |- | 2018 | Matal | Ontu | |} ==References== ==External links== * Category:Living people Category:Bangladeshi film actresses Category:Actresses in Bengali cinema Category:People from Shariatpur District Category:Bangladeshi actresses Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
